        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/b2d939/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2024-07-14T00:57:04.974Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Currently, when scrolling through conversations, the top section (including the app header and possibly other elements) remains static. It would greatly enhance user experience if this top section could elegantly hide as the user scrolls down, providing more screen real estate for viewing conversations. This feature would streamline the interface and create a more immersive chatting experience.</p>",
